s=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1113e4d52c77205511a5fd5035cbc8ea80455e6f","tid":85204,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不應<br />\n除非你想身敗名裂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對⋯⋯我要想辦法解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會身敗名裂"},{"pid":"c6be0fc1c57d49dc3a73058f363d9e5544424739","tid":85204,"uid":39907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不應<br />\n除非你想身敗名裂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對⋯⋯我要想辦法解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會身敗名裂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能個客唔識 執到一pat屎咁 出到街只會入攝影師數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f394d436edfc7a627e8a8e3da11fffaa1d09f3d","tid":85204,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:53:36.000Z","msg":"後期是攝影的一部份"},{"pid":"65b16f6ac8c1ab14b3da81eb12492d60d98e0d59","tid":85204,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對⋯⋯我要想辦法解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會身敗名裂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能個客唔識 執到一pat屎咁 出到街只會入攝影師數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncrop到成pat屎都已經死得"},{"pid":"3aca2d94fcfeff3241a8eb30b81313a81246baf4","tid":85204,"uid":36658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點解會身敗名裂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能個客唔識 執到一pat屎咁 出到街只會入攝影師數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncrop到成pat屎都已經死得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最慘係個攝影師嗰邊佢地執到一pat屎咁<br />\n張相係畢業班相黎 今日我一收到真係嚇出黎 個個人樣都紅到好似醉晒酒咁 wb又錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂佢我美好既中學回憶就咁糟蹋左 所以我都諗緊可唔可以問佢拎返raw自己執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76551c23f591b1eaf68cc79d2bdc6ee9e902dd84","tid":85204,"uid":28604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>攝影師應否把Raw檔給客人自行retouch?</blockquote><br />\n除非佢特別要求 正常我都係出jpg比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實就算出jpg，我都唔想俾佢自己retouch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好似係控制唔到⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n一係合約講明 佢retouch就要比我睇左先<br />\n唔係唔好出我名"},{"pid":"b2d46ce0655273e222fee1b11e91be311fe34095","tid":85204,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"有時會預左RAW執光暗專登under<br />\n俾張RAW人人地見到咁撚黑以為你唔識影相"},{"pid":"5076b38611c729aa7745cd4b50000e0236be0a71","tid":85204,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"梗係不應啦"},{"pid":"3aeebb0afd6ef9ac225f131d2b5077f08cd315cb","tid":85204,"uid":54818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"你出去食飯會唔會叫廚師淨係準備哂材料比你，然後你自己煮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8611f40483406da73114545b26a63d14e1805b","tid":85204,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>攝影師應否把Raw檔給客人自行retouch?</blockquote><br />\n除非佢特別要求 正常我都係出jpg比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實就算出jpg，我都唔想俾佢自己retouch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好似係控制唔到⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係商業用，得罪講句影相佬識撚執咩， 比番專業既designer做啦， 你唔撚識亂執又要人幫你跟手尾"},{"pid":"e8a75ef184289046482c0b0f6c1b8b6beba8eaf1","tid":85204,"uid":8909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n除非佢特別要求 正常我都係出jpg比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實就算出jpg，我都唔想俾佢自己retouch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好似係控制唔到⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係商業用，得罪講句影相佬識撚執咩， 比番專業既designer做啦， 你唔撚識亂執又要人幫你跟手尾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同陳生意見<br />\nDesigner 個perspective 真係同photographer 有d 唔同<br />\n唔係邊個叻唔個唔識執<br />\n係出o黎個product 能唔能夠達到想要o既效果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80c714391711659031b3ad0c04369dc36468cf0","tid":85204,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n除非佢特別要求 正常我都係出jpg比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實就算出jpg，我都唔想俾佢自己retouch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好似係控制唔到⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係商業用，得罪講句影相佬識撚執咩， 比番專業既designer做啦， 你唔撚識亂執又要人幫你跟手尾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同陳生意見<br />\nDesigner 個perspective 真係同photographer 有d 唔同<br />\n唔係邊個叻唔個唔識執<br />\n係出o黎個product 能唔能夠達到想要o既效果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十年前都己經係咁啦D photop 又唔識又要攪有D又執到鬼五馬六, 獲獲要人執手尾, 有位大師D仲醒到攪埋自己profile(影大牌子既,不過我知佢改profile用黎呃個客話要執相加錢), 次次都要同佢地講影完相千奇唔好攪佢, 用lightroom個D比人tune下相扮下攝影師就得, 執相跟本唔係個回事, 執就係要執番好佢，唔係個D白痴改到變晒色又偏色呢樣個樣加D effect就以為好有feel既野"},{"pid":"dc264cf5e18fcc67f4bed28c3f563bb4904b9955","tid":85204,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e160b4d34ad4fd7d8221519361947aad1548a3c2","tid":85204,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"影相佬扮咩攝影師"},{"pid":"d794cf3b7169f25c09ab66b8d1ce54db719e233b","tid":85204,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"戇鳩，一定唔畀"},{"pid":"dd5d4176d831f6e778ec632cf509327e0435a526","tid":85204,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"Raw檔係未完成品<br />\n你比得人就預左有風險<br />\n正如我就算比draft客仔睇我都一定加水印<br />\n保障雙方啫<br />\n<br />\n利申被拖數過2年 已放棄"}]}